<https://w3id.org/mqto#readBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Relates a Signal (data channel) to the Metric that is computed from it (specified layer). Inverse of mqto:readsFrom. For the actual-layer counterpart see mqto:evaluatedBy."@en .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#readBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "read by"@en .
