<https://w3id.org/mqto#completionTime> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "completion time"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/mqto#endTime
<https://w3id.org/mqto#endTime> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#endTime> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#endTime> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "end time"@en .
