<https://w3id.org/mqto#ActualIshikawaItem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Abstract superclass for actual/instance layer counterparts of IshikawaItem. Integrates SOSA: each ActualIshikawaItem is a FeatureOfInterest that can be observed, has ObservableProperties, and can have FailureOccurrences. In die-casting (dga ontology), concrete instances include specific die-casting cells, material batches, and production runs."@en .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#ActualIshikawaItem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Actual Ishikawa Item"@en .
