<https://w3id.org/mqto#CountermeasureExecution> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The actual execution of a Countermeasure procedure, performed to mitigate one or more FailureOccurrences. Links to the Countermeasure specification via lis:implements (LIS pattern) and tracks which specific failures were addressed. As a subclass of pko:ProcedureExecution, countermeasure executions align with PKO's procedure execution model while maintaining LIS actual/specified semantics. Note: Does not directly subclass lis:Activity (which is lis:Specified), but implements Countermeasure (which is lis:Activity), maintaining the LIS distinction between specified and actual layers."@en .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#CountermeasureExecution> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Countermeasure Execution"@en .
