<https://w3id.org/mqto#Machine> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://rds.posccaesar.org/ontology/lis14/rdl/PhysicalArtefact> .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#Machine> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/mqto#IshikawaItem> .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#Machine> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> _:genid38 .
