<https://w3id.org/mqto#Machine> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Manufacturing equipment, tools, and devices (the 'M' in Ishikawa's Machine). Represents specified physical resources that participate in Methods. In die-casting, dg:Aggregate represents machines like die-casting cells, furnaces, and robots. Machines provide Signals (sensor readings, control channels) and can have associated Failures and Metrics."@en .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#Machine> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Machine"@en .
