<https://w3id.org/mqto#MaterialChunk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Actual material instance, the instance-layer counterpart of Material. Represents specific batches, lots, or quantities of material with identifiers, composition data, and quality measurements. In die-casting (dga ontology), examples include specific aluminum alloy batches with batch numbers, chemical composition, and temperature observations."@en .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#MaterialChunk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Material Chunk"@en .
