<https://w3id.org/mqto#PhysicalMachine> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Actual machine instance, the instance-layer counterpart of Machine. Represents specific physical equipment with serial numbers, operational history, and sensor data. In die-casting (dga ontology), examples include specific die-casting cells (e.g., 'Cell_TCG_200'), furnaces, and robots with concrete observation data."@en .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#PhysicalMachine> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Physical Machine"@en .
